---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Full Stack Development</h2>
		<p>React, Node.js, Express, TypeScript, MongoDB, REST & GraphQL APIs — building scalable, production-ready web apps.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="pencil-line" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Technical Writing</h2>
		<p>8+ years documenting APIs, SDKs, and developer workflows — turning complex systems into clear, usable guides.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="strategy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>AI-Driven Engineering</h2>
		<p>Building with GPT, Claude, and Gemini — from RAG pipelines to AI-assisted coding and LLM documentation.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999);
		border-top: 3px solid var(--accent-regular);
		transition: box-shadow var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.box:hover {
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.skills p {
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		color: var(--gray-300);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-xl);
		}
	}
</style>
